verse: Unto thee, O Lord, do I lift up my soul.
Unto thee, O Lord, do I lift up my soul.
O my God, I trust in thee, let me not be
ashamed, let not mine enemies triumph over me.
Yea, let none that wait, on thee be
ashamed. Yea, let none that wait, on thee
be ashamed, O my God, trust in thee, let
Me not be ashamed, let not mine enemies
Remember not, the sins of my youth.
Remeraber not, the sins of my youth.
O My God, trust in thee, let me not be
I ashamed, let not mine enemies triumph
